'''Hospital Punta Pacifica''' is a [[hospital]] in [[Panama City]], [[Panama]]. It is the only hospital in Central America to be affiliated with [[Johns Hopkins Medicine International]]. <ref>http://www.hospitalpuntapacifica.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=section&layout=blog&id=9&Itemid=27&lang=en</ref>. Attracting [[medical tourism]] is a major component of its operating plan.<ref>http://www.hospitalpuntapacifica.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=82&Itemid=28&lang=en</ref>

